= \sqrt{\left\langle \begin{pmatrix} 2 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix}, \begin{pmatrix} 2 \\ 0 \end{pmatrix} \right\rangle}
= \sqrt{2^2 + 0^2}
= \sqrt{4}
= 2.00
\end{equation}\]

